# Primary Color

***Choose a color for all buttons on the application***

---

This SmartApp ***Color*** is fully customizable, you just have to choose a dominant ***Color*** and we take care of deriving it into as much ***Color*** as the application needs to display nicely and consistently with your choice!

Anyway, we suggest you use a dark toned ***Color*** as it will be derived mostly in brighter color and a too bright dominant ***Color*** will result in a lack of readability in some of the sub-elements.

This customization is a good way to brand the FocusApp according to your company / group identity, take advantage of it!

The best way to decide on a primary ***Color*** is to think about the vibe of your product or service, and peruse ***Colors*** that fit that vibe to find one you like. Here are some examples:
<li> <b>Red:</b>  Implies excitement or happiness</li>
<li><b> Orange:</b> Implies a friendly, fun time is ahead</li>
<li> <b>Yellow:</b> Implies optimism and happiness</li>
<li><b>Green:</b>  Implies freshness and nature</li>
<li><b>Blue:</b>  Implies dependability and reassurance</li>
<li><b>Purple:</b>  Implies a distinguished brand that has a history of quality</li>
<li><b>Brown:</b> Implies a reliable product that can be used by anyone</li>
<li><b>Black:</b> Implies luxury or elegance</li>
<li><b>White:</b> Implies sleek, user-friendly products</li>
